Allen Hoskins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Allen_Hoskins 0 Allen Clayton Hoskins (August 9, 1920 – July 26, 1980) was an American child actor, most famous for portraying the character of Farina in 105 Our Gang short films from 1922 to 1931.
